### Scriptoryum API - Testes de Autenticação

### 1. Registrar novo usuário
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "usuario_teste",
  "email": "teste@scriptoryum.com",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123",
  "confirmPassword": "MinhaSenh@123"
}

### 2. Fazer login
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@scriptoryum.com",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### 3. Obter informações do usuário autenticado (substitua {token} pelo token JWT recebido)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### 4. Validar token
GET https://localhost:7000/api/auth/validate-token
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### 5. Renovar token
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

"{token}"

### 6. Obter perfil do usuário
GET https://localhost:7000/api/account/profile
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### 7. Atualizar perfil
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/account/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
  "userName": "novo_usuario",
  "email": "novo@scriptoryum.com"
}

### 8. Alterar senha
POST https://localhost:7000/api/account/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
  "currentPassword": "MinhaSenh@123",
  "newPassword": "NovaSenha@456",
  "confirmNewPassword": "NovaSenha@456"
}

### 9. Listar documentos do usuário
GET https://localhost:7000/api/account/documents
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### 10. Excluir conta (cuidado!)
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/account/delete-account
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

"MinhaSenh@123"

### Exemplo de uso com token real:
### Substitua o token abaixo por um token válido obtido do login

# @token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### Teste com token real
GET https://localhost:7000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}